name: Suckable Objects
description:
This game was made in 28 hours, as part of Forsbergs Gamejam Nov. 2019, under the theme "Dark Matter".

Feed your black hole as many items as you can! Make it grow larger and larger, and CONSUME THE WHOLE WORLD!!! (if you have the golf skills to pull it off...)

Made by:
Max Robert, (www.maxrobertstudios.com, https://maxrobertstudios.itch.io/)
Edward Sedelius,
Yunis Al-breihi 
Axel Marelius.
